OL,3,CCovid victim's daughter says
OL,4,Clegislative change needed over
OL,5,Chospital visits
OL,7,FThere must be legislative change to
OL,8,Fensure that elderly and vulnerable
OL,9,Fpatients do not die alone in hospital,
OL,10,Fa bereaved daughter has told the Covid-
OL,11,F19 Inquiry.
OL,13,FMartina Ferguson told the hearing that
OL,14,Fshe had to argue with healthcare staff
OL,15,Ffor access to a hospital Covid ward in
OL,16,Fthe days before her mother died in
OL,17,F2021.
