OL,7,FMs Ferguson, a founding member of the
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland Covid-19 Bereaved
OL,9,FFamilies for Justice group, was the
OL,10,Ffinal witness to give evidence to
OL,11,Fmodule three of the inquiry, which is
OL,12,Fexamining the impact of the pandemic
OL,13,Fon healthcare systems across the UK.
OL,15,FHer mother Ursula Derry died aged 88
OL,16,Ffrom Covid-19 in January 2021 at
OL,17,FCraigavon Area Hospital.
