OL,7,FThe inquiry heard that Ms Derry was
OL,8,Fmoved to the hospital from a care home
OL,9,Fjust before Christmas 2020 suffering
OL,10,Ffrom a high heart rate.
OL,12,FMs Ferguson said she discovered later
OL,13,Fthe same evening that her mother had
OL,14,Falso contracted Covid.
OL,16,FShe was transferred to the hospital's
OL,17,FCovid ward on Christmas Eve.
