OL,4,Clegislative change needed over
OL,5,Chospital visits
OL,7,FMs Ferguson said when she went to
OL,8,Faccompany her mother onto the ward,
OL,9,Fbut was told by a nurse that family
OL,10,Fmembers were not permitted.
OL,12,FShe said: "I told them 'I am my
OL,13,Fmummy's care partner. I am not sure if
OL,14,Fyou are familiar with the guidance but
OL,15,Fyou should be'.
OL,17,F"At that time, the care partner
OL,18,Fguidance was endorsed and released by
OL,19,Fthe Department of Health and the
OL,20,F(Northern Ireland) Executive."
