OL,7,FMr Ferguson said she was then told she
OL,8,Fwas allowed into the ward for one hour
OL,9,Fto help feed her mother.
OL,11,FShe added: "I hope no other families
OL,12,Ffeel distressed because I know not a
OL,13,Flot of other families got into the
OL,14,FCovid ward."
OL,16,FHer mother died on January 4.
OL,18,FAsked what she wanted the inquiry to
OL,19,Fconsider, Ms Ferguson said: "What we
OL,20,Fare looking at is a legislative change.
