OL,3,CCovid victim's daughter says
OL,4,Clegislative change needed over
OL,5,Chospital visits
OL,7,F"We have contacted the First Minister
OL,8,F(Michelle O'Neill) and deputy First
OL,9,FMinister Emma Little-Pengelly. I would
OL,10,Fhope our group will be allowed to meet
OL,11,Fwith them and they will make change
OL,12,Fhappen.
OL,14,F"I was campaigning before my mummy
OL,15,Fdied, after my mummy died, for the
OL,16,Fcare partner guidance.
OL,18,F"You will have heard during this
OL,19,Finquiry that was rolled out in care
OL,20,Fhomes in September 2020. It was
OL,21,Fextended in hospitals in February 2022.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
