OL,3,CCovid victim's daughter says
OL,4,Clegislative change needed over
OL,5,Chospital visits
OL,7,F"I want that on a legislative footing.
OL,8,FWhen you have a member of the
OL,9,FDepartment of Health and an email
OL,10,Fwhich says guidance is guidance, that
OL,11,Fis not good enough.
OL,13,F"We need to see a legislative change.
OL,14,FWe need to make sure that nobody dies
OL,15,Falone ever again.
OL,17,F"It is so important their family is
OL,18,Fwith them."
